"Podo empregar &kmail; xunto cun cliente de correo distinto, &eg; "
"<application>mutt</application>?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:325
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you're using the mbox format for your folders it is not possible to "
#| "use a different email client while &kmail; is running. With "
